            "creation_date": 1400253050,
            "body": "<p>You create a new instance of <code>BasketContainer<\/code> every time, so that new instances will have a new clear ArrayList.<\/p>\n\n<p>To fix it you should create your <code>BasketContainer<\/code> instance somewhere (maybe in an init block?) and save the reference, then use it to add the elements.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 23698746,
            "question_id": 23698711,
            "last_edit_date": 1402760185
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/1pefW.png?s=256",
                "account_id": 2529002,
