            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1400253066,
            "creation_date": 1400253066,
            "body": "<p>You're creating a new <code>BasketContainer<\/code> within the scope of the method.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>BasketContainer bc = new BasketContainer();\nbc.addProduct(prod);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>The <code>addToBasket<\/code> method should call <code>addProduct<\/code> on a field of the class it's in.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 23698751,
            "question_id": 23698711
        }
